a-boheme-alla-choregies-orange/" rel="next">&#8220;La Bohème&#8221; alla Choregies Orange <span class="meta-nav">&rarr;</span></a></span> </nav><nav class="nav-single-hidden"> <span class="nav-previous"></span> <span class="nav-next"></span><div class="clear"></div> </nav></div><div class="comments-block box-shadow-2px clearfix"><div id="comments" class="comments-area"><h2 class="comments-title"> 2 comments</h2><ol class="commentlist"><li class="comment even thread-even depth-1" id="li-comment-15391"> <article id="comment-15391" class="comment clearfix"> <header class="comment-meta comment-author vcard"><div class="comment-avatar"><img src="http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/ed96c087bbdf553346b8dc4ee9fec170?s=75&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g" width="75" height="75" alt="" class="avatar avatar-75wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-75 alignnone photo avatar-default" /></div><cite class="fn">michele.macaluso@fastwebnet.it</cite><a class="comment-meta-time muted-small" href="http://www.gbopera.it/2012/07/xxxviii-festival-della-valle-ditria-artaserse-di-hasse/#comment-15391"><time datetime="2012-07-18T10:43:07+00:00">18 luglio 2012 at 10:43</time></a> </header> <section class="comment-content comment"><p>Lavia torni al suo mestiere!!!!(leggi teatro)</p> </section><div class="reply clearfix"></div> </article></li><li class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1" id="li-comment-15393"> <article id="comment-15393" class="comment clearfix"> <header class="comment-meta comment-author vcard"><div class="comment-avatar"><img src="http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/b5c654a208cf3b21f07fc85af0d498c3?s=75&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g" width="75" height="75" alt="" class="avatar avatar-75wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-75 alignnone photo avatar-default" /></div><cite class="fn">Isabella Chiappara</cite><a class="comment-meta-time muted-small" href="http://www.gbopera.it/2012/07/xxxviii-festival-della-valle-ditria-artaserse-di-hasse/#comment-15393"><time datetime="2012-07-18T13:07:25+00:00">18 luglio 2012 at 13:07</time></a> </header> <section class="comment-content comment"><p>Sono fondamentalmente d&#8217;accordo sulla lettura critica dell&#8217;interpretazione:la Prina ha veramente giganteggiato, soprattutto nel finale del II atto, la Schiavo invece l&#8217;ho trovata brava sì, ma un pò monocorde, non in grado di rendere le gamme degli affetti pienamente. Io ho solo ascoltato la diretta radio, ma ho trovato l&#8217;intervista a Lavia, presupponente e fondamentale ignaro di cosa sia un&#8217;opera sera barocca, blaterando una serie di luoghi comuni e castronerie sulla stessa. Il fatto è che Lavia fa guai pure a teatro!!!</p> </section><div class="reply clearfix"></div> </article></li></ol><div id="respond" class="comment-respond"><h3 id="reply-title" class="comment-reply-title">Lascia un commento <small><a rel="nofollow" id="cancel-comment-reply-link" href="/2012/07/xxxviii-festival-della-valle-ditria-artaserse-di-hasse/#respond" style="display:none;">Annulla risposta</a></small></h3><form action="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-comments-post.php" method="post" id="commentform" class="comment-form"><p class="comment-notes"><span id="email-notes">Il tuo indirizzo email non sarà pubblicato.</span> I campi obbligatori sono contrassegnati <span class="required">*</span></p><p class="comment-form-comment"><label for="comment">Commento</label><textarea id="comment" name="comment" cols="45" rows="8" maxlength="65525" aria-required="true" required="required"></textarea></p><p class="comment-form-author"><label for="author">Nome <span class="required">*</span></label> <input id="author" name="author" type="text" value="" size="30" maxlength="245" aria-required='true' required='required' /></p><p class="comment-form-email"><label for="email">Email <span class="required">*</span></label> <input id="email" name="email" type="text" value="" size="30" maxlength="100" aria-describedby="email-notes" aria-required='true' required='required' /></p><p class="comment-form-url"><label for="url">Sito web</label> <input id="url" name="url" type="text" value="" size="30" maxlength="200" /></p><p class="form-submit"><input name="submit" type="submit" id="submit" class="submit" value="Commento all&#039;articolo" /> <input type='hidden' name='comment_post_ID' value='37736' id='comment_post_ID' /> <input type='hidden' name='comment_parent' id='comment_parent' value='0' /></p><p style="display: none;"><input type="hidden" id="akismet_comment_nonce" name="akismet_comment_nonce" value="93a5552c38" /></p><p style="display: none;"><input type="hidden" id="ak_js" name="ak_js" value="196"/></p></form></div></div></div></div></div><div id="secondary" class="widget-area span4 sb-4" role="complementary"> <aside id="search-4" class="widget widget_search clearfix"><h3 class="widget-title">RICERCA</h3><form method="get" id="searchform" action="http://www.gbopera.it/"> <label for="s" class="assistive-text">Search</label> <input type="text" class="field" name="s" id="s" placeholder="Search" /> <button type="submit" class="submit btn" name="submit" id="searchsubmit"><i class="icon-search"></i></button></form> </aside><aside id="ct-relatedposts-widget-2" class="widget ct-relatedposts-widget clearfix"><h3 class="widget-title">Articoli correlati</h3><ul class="related-posts-single clearfix"><li> <a href='http://www.gbopera.it/2016/07/martina-franca-42-festival-della-valle-ditria-la-grotta-di-trofonio/' title='Martina Franca, 42° Festival della Valle d&#8217;Itria: &#8220;La grotta di Trofonio&#8221;'><img width="70" height="70" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/1K8A1319-70x70.jpg" class="attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="la grotta di Trofonio, Martina Franca 2016" title="Martina Franca, 42° Festival della Valle d&#8217;Itria: &#8220;La grotta di Trofonio&#8221;" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/1K8A1319-70x70.jpg 70w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/1K8A1319-75x75.jpg 75w" sizes="(max-width: 70px) 100vw, 70